					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12447220#post-4380544</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12447220/scp-4365#post-4380544</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2019 04:06:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>This is normal.</p> </blockquote> <p>God, the energy in this dialogue is astounding. I'm a tad confused by the ending; how is it that this former employee has managed to live in our world without realizing something is up? Either there's some weird twist implied here that the interviewers crossed into the other world that I'm just not getting, or these other people don't operate as rationally as us. Given the on-the-nose insistence that &quot;this is normal&quot;, I'm inclined to think the latter?</p> <p>Weirdly intriguing, would love to see how tales about this.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
